      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any scratches, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather upholstery and trim showing no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history available. This is a rare opportunity to own a car that has been kept in such pristine, like-new condition.",
