    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior has several large dents, noticeable rust spots along the wheel wells, and the clear coat is peeling on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears in the seating and a persistent musty odor. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly, the transmission slips between second and third gear, and the brakes are near the end of their life. It currently starts and drives, but I would recommend towing it or performing immediate maintenance before any long trips. This is a project car or a candidate for parts, sold strictly as-is.",
      "price": 6500.0,
